cretlerin <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">01/11/2021 tarihi saat 08.00 den itibaren uygulanacağı</span> bildirilmiştir.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Yapılan artışa ait yeni ücret tarifesi aşağıdaki çizelgede bulunmaktadır.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Bilgilerinize rica ederim.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dursun CİN</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Başkan</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">GENEL YAZI: (299 )</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Not:</span> Tarife yürürlülük tarihi olan 01.11.2021 tarihinde NBS’de otomatik olarak yayımlanacaktır.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left; background: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;\">01.11.2021 tarihinden itibaren geçerli Tebligat Ücretleri</span></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 0 0 0;\"><table style=\"width:100%; border:none; border-spacing:0; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">TEBLİGATLAR (Adli, İdari, Vergi</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">ve diğer)</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:100px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Yurtiçi tebligat ücretleri</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:355px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">A) &nbsp; TEBLİGAT</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:100px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td rowspan=\"6\"  style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:355px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1- &nbsp; &nbsp;  </span>Telgraf ile yapılacak tebliğ evrakı normal veya acele telgraf işaretiyle kabul edilir.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2-</span> Telgraf ile yapılacak tebliğ evrakından ilk kademe hızlı tebligat ücretine ilaveten tarifesine göre telgraf ücreti alınır.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3-</span> Değer konulmuş veya Sigortalı olarak verilen tebliğ evrakından tebliğ ücretine ilaveten değerlendirme ücreti alınır.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4-</span> Tebligatlardan adreste (Konutta) teslim ve uçak özel hizmet ücreti alınmaz.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 100 Grama kadar</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:100px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">26,00</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 250 Grama kadar</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:100px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">35,00</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 500 Grama kadar</p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; width:100px; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_Normal\" style=\"text-align: left;\">37,00</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:solid thin #000000;\"><p class=\"p_No